name: Wisata Puncak JR Jembrana Bali
address: Banjar Pancaseming Desa Batuagung, Kecamatan Jembrana, Batuagung, Kec. Jembrana, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82218, Indonesia
review 1: Best view ever. Go by motorcycle, it's safer. But it's stunning. Not really a busy place. Therefore, a must go if you pass this Area.
review 2: Nice place, almost no tourism and the viewpoint looks well cared for.  Entrance is 5000 IDR per person.
review 4: a very beautiful place and the scenery is fabulous
review 5: Love this place, not easy to reach but it worth the trip. The best time is at sunset, but also during the day the view is stunning. The family near there made a good job, the platform seems solid, the steps are regular and they built a really nice garden around
